  10-19  Loans (4)
    pg 125  #4.21

(comparing loans with various interest rates)
Write a program that lets the user enter the loan amount and loan period in
number of years and siplays the monthly and total payments for each interest
rate starting from 5% to 8%, with an increment of 1/8. Suppose you enter the
amount 10,000 for five years; display a table as follows:

-- loan summary: ----------------------------------------------
Loan Amount:       10000
Number of Years:   5
---------------------------------------------------------------
(%) Interest Rate     ($) Monthly Payment     ($) Total Payment
5                     188.71                  11322.74     
5.125                 189.28                  11357.13     
5.25                  189.85                  11391.59     
...                   ...                     ...          
7.85                  202.16                  12129.97     
8.0                   202.76                  12165.83     
---------------------------------------------------------------
